translations.welcome-text-1: This project provides the ability to send requests to the <0>"Rick and Morty API"</0> and get data using GraphQL.
translations.welcome-text-2: <0>RS School</0> is free-of-charge and community-based education program conducted by The Rolling Scopes developer community since 2013.
translations.welcome-text-3: Everyone can study at RS School, regardless of age, professional employment, or place of residence. The mentors and trainers of our school are front-end and javascript developers from different companies and countries.
